name: Blox Competition Adjustable Fuel Pressure Regulator
description:
The BLOX Racing Competition 2-Port adjustable FPRs are designed to offer high performance and reliability.  Each FPR unit comes pre-assembled from BLOX and is guaranteed to offer consistency each time the engine is turned on. 

These billet aluminum units feature -6AN inlet and return ports in-line which offers more flexibility during installation, 1/8" NPT ports, are compatible with gasoline, diesel, methanol and ethanol.

BLOX Competition Adj. FPRs are designed to work with aftermarket fuel rails and are available in an assortment of color combinations.


Specifications

Inlet size: -6AN
Max. flow: 2.5 GPM @ 25 PSID
Adj. range: 25-90 PSID

Free Shipping

name: Blox Coolant Expansion Tanks
description:
BLOX Racing coolant expansion tanks are designed to catch coolant overflow and properly re-circulate it back to the radiator.  The proper re-circulation ensures that your engine continues to operate at safe temperatures.

BLOX Racing coolant expansion tanks are manufactured using high quality stainless steel.  Unlike aluminum, the fully polished body resists corrosion and stains.

A must have for cleaning up your engine bay. 

Available in two size 2x15 26oz
and 3x10 34 oz

name: Honda/Acura Fuel Feed Hard line Adapter No Flare Black
description:
If your looking to covert your stock hard line to use AN fittings & hose then this is the fitting you need. Unlike the other hard line adapters in the market, ours is rated to 300psi. Simply cut your steel hard line using a plumbing pipe cutter, insert socket, then ferrule, and last tighten the male fitting to the socket. No flaring need.

Works with hard lines with a diameter of 8mm or 5/16".

 Note: This works for the feed side only, it will not work for the return line.
